Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:40.10,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:10.19,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:34.76,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:17.40,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.43,0:23:29.47,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:01.50,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sense a powerful light inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the power of your newly obtained Sun Arcana is the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard the "Long-Nosed Song"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Vel-Vel, vel, velvet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My master has a long nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to sing that song with my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It truly takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The main events of the culture festival have been concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Festival committee staff, assemble in the A/V Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet! So, what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna grab a bite to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good! The Prince of Junes can treat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Why don't we have the two Miss Yasogami winners treat us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you ask a maiden to pay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your heart!{I'll shoot through your heart!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call yourself a maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can we all just forget about the contest? Really, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, wouldn't it be a shame to just call it a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, you came to the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! I got some stir-fry noodles!{LOCALIZATIONSHIT}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I danced, went to the haunted house, and even saw the fortune-teller!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw the fortune-teller?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, this pretty lady said you're a, um... uh, play...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a play-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pla-Player!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She said you're a natural player.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a hard time finding you, but I'm glad we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to be at the prefectural office early tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have to head out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to house-sit with Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Senpai}Oh, are you leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can watch the house by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, Nanako! I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana's a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you and your brother stay with me tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-What?! Yuki, what's {\i1}that{\i0} about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why don't you spend the night with me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're partying at the inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Nanako—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sweet! We're staying at the inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I only invited—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we eat eggs boiled in the hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just for the night? I should inform my grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.04,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot spring, yukata, and flushed skin! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, it's Naoto. Mr. Yakushiji, is Grandpa available?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Teddie! You're being gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a slumber party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll all have fun together, okay? So you should come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go! I'll spend the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I better go home and pick up a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all gather up at the Amagi Inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,On second thought, I'll head out after I stop by—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kasai, we'll be staying the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we're such a large group.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. We've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Yuki, you're the steamy young mistress of the hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not! I'm just a waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but a large party suddenly showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, you should leave that group to me and enjoy the time you have with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you need help for the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to escort you to your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'd appreciate it... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She helps out from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? But what about Aiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your room is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a tad bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think softer colors would be visually relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Senpai}She's kinda cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take some out and—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So they aren't putting us all in one room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I could handle it if they were next door, but they're so bear-y far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, most of the rooms are full, so the girls are on a different floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr!{assuming this is Teddie}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, we've really slept together a lot these past six months.{note to self: change to homosexual double entendre after seeing the scene with video}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The tent, the hotel, and now the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You got changed quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your meal is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So full!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Any problems with your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna play trump?{?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls said they're hitting the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the bath co-ed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm not into bathing a zillion times a day}I don't like bathing more than I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You cool with hitting the baths once before bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, got any idea what's up with this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks really expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You noticed that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't normally see a room like this open during the busy season.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd almost forgotten about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think something happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why did everyone suddenly get so quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,K-K-Kanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you guys so afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear! Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that the open-air bath is practically empty right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That panicking really worked up a sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go rinse it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to bathing with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1237.5,1044)}We'll face the same direction as\Nwe wash each others' backs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1237.5,1044)}and sing songs while\Nstaring at Mt. Fuji, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This world is full of so many fun things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be here without you, Master. Thank you.{rank up}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the elevator's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto, come on over! There's plenty of room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto, your skin's so smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! It's so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky you! Your skin's like porcelain and your hair's silky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sto— Hey! Don't touch me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be okay spending the night here? Aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun! I'm always home alone until Big Bro gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good at staying home alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm alone, I don't open the door for any strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I hold down the fort!{FORESHADOWING}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Nanako. Would you like to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing it since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You still do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, "No," Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's race to the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Loser has to buy fruit lattes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer a Cielo Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Am I racing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so big! I'll show you my bear-paddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}my{\i0} line!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, no, no! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, ow, ow! Damn that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This situation is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Scumbags!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We should gather up our courage and stand our ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the point in showing off our courage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Peeping is a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We'll have to punish them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! You sure got them good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not half bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they saw anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This bath is open for men right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the times confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't {"Aha ha ha" me}give me that. Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a great bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we take another dip later?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's open 24 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so feel free to whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A moment please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's those men from the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:12:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked, and the open-air bath is supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to be open for guys right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're absolutely horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I hadn't misjudged when we should retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't your fault, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, did you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Nothing good ever happens to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do something to clear my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked up a nice sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go wash it off in the other bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.09,0:12:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Moron! If the open-air bath is open to guys, this one's open to chicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Owie, owie, owie! My head's getting all lumpy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already turned your program down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to take that tone with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss "High School Heiress to a Cursed Inn."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What cursed inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there where Yamano Mayumi stayed before she got killed and strung upside down?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost customers since then, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought up an awesome idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"A High School Girl's Embarrassing Battle to Save the Cursed Inn!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain further.{I fail to see what you're getting at.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love for you to play the lead, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There'd be a steamy scene of you in the hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're trying to boost your popularity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to get more customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As the inn's heiress, I think you're capable of making the intelligent decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, "traditional" just means that it's "old."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The food's bland, and the portions stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to "sell yourself" if you want to attract customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Cursed Inn Where the Late Announcer Spent Her Last Night!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're screwed because you don't use this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of your degrading remarks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to ever let you take footage of our inn for your program!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's how you're going to be, I'll air that spiteful remark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Air it as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll complain to your show's sponsors if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Couldn't that cause us trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still recording, moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!{Toodles!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I said some incredible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they with a TV station?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you guys chase away those reporter jerks?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki chased them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd want to rely on creeps who peep on girls bathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, about that! The open-air bath was open to dudes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your fault, you know!{You're the ones at fault here!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's hear an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't change the fact that you peeped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to falsely classify us as perverts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie, Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you perverts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!{note to self: check to see who says this}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Women sure are scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We never did get to take our baths.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, absolutely nothing good ever happens to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, will you?{senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I heard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There isn't one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,O-One... One what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember now after hearing those guys from the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What? I don't remember anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... this is the room where the late Miss Yamano stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You just had to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I managed to forget! But you just had to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, after dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Any problems with your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Amagi! She pulled a fast one on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! First the bath and now this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally screwing us over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go to sleep in a room that's haunted!{like this! (at a time like this)}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind! I'm going to stay with Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to relax and sleep if I'm not gazing into their sleeping faces! {tempted to write feaces}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Sleeping faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sneaking into their room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies, good morning to you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Candid Early Bird Camera"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Scratch that. It's "Caught Asleep"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your guide, Reporter Teddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you put that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I get nervous without it, so I always bring it with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit talking like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...a brush! It has long hair in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you're getting into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a brush, but not just any brush! It's a toothbrush!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a faint minty scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! Now {\i1}I'm{\i0} starting to get excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but Nanako's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay! Nana is {big-hearted.}nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave her out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to wake her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally made it to their beds! They're sound asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, I'm scared of ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oomph.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right! I'll prove to you that I'm a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Satonaka, please be gentle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't go for Naoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Aren't they short some futons?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh darn, what gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, you had a thing for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you should've said so sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such naughty boys.{this is more terrifying than Another}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,M-M-M-Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just crying our eyes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought there weren't any men out there who appreciated a real woman's charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Come on over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't tell anyone about this, you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was something no man was ever meant to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound asleep with Naoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good ever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sowwy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you always up this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have to prepare for tomorrow and study for my license.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What license?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be nice to do something extra to help the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how I met my Shadow after I got thrown into the TV world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was shown how, deep down, I felt like I was a bird trapped in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was all in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided to open the door to the cage on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That resolve is what let you defeat your Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I realized it's okay for me to follow my own desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I had considered leaving and living by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But strangely enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,once I opened the door and looked back,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized how dear this place is to me, and now I want to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I realized sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had struck out on my own, I know I would've regretted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become completely self-sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I was being presumptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the inn, my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and the waitresses and chefs who made me the person I am today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think of it that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,my problems aren't just my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm choosing to stay here by my own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the time I've spent with you and the others has helped me realize all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a good thing by getting rid of those guys from the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! I was afraid you'd think ill of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted a soft drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a letter for you in the mail, Big Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the truth about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been locked up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The case is still on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.85,0:24:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn brat, you aren't getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.60,0:24:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.89,0:24:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Let's play a whole bunch!
